                str: "Landing pages usually take 3 to 7 days. More complex projects may take 2 to 4 weeks."
            },
            {
                q: "Do you offer maintenance after delivery?",
                a: "Yes. We offer web maintenance plans including ",
                str: "support, updates, security, and performance improvements."
            },
            {
                q: "Can I request changes after the initial design?",
                a: "Of course. ",
                str: "All projects include revisions to ensure the final result matches your brand."
            },
            {
                q: "Do you handle SEO and speed optimization?",
                a: "Yes. ",
                str: "All projects include technical SEO and performance optimization."
            },
            {
                q: "Do you build e-commerce websites?",
                a: "Yes. ",
                str: "We create conversion-optimized online stores with carts and payment gateways."
            },
            {
                q: "Do you work with companies and startups?",
                a: "Yes. ",
                str: "We work with entrepreneurs, startups, and companies aiming to grow digitally."
            },
            {
                q: "What technologies do you use?",
                a: "We use modern technologies like ",
                str: "Astro, React, Tailwind, Node.js, and secure databases."
            },
            {
                q: "Will my website be responsive?",
                a: "Yes. ",
                str: "All our projects are fully responsive."
            },
            {
                q: "Can my project scale in the future?",
                a: "Yes. ",
                str: "We design scalable solutions that grow with your business."
            },
            {
                q: "How can I request a quote?",
                a: "Contact us via the ",
                str: "form or WhatsApp for a personalized quote."
            },
        ],
    },
};

const t = i18n[lang];
